      <event start="T857-814" end="T859-368">A majčken žakelj? </event>
      <event start="T861-279" end="T334">Aja, </event>
      <event start="T334" end="T189">pol bi mogla kupiti enega zgodnjega, </event>
      <event start="T189" end="T864-333">da je čim prej? </event>
      <event start="T864-333" end="T865-811">Pa enega kasnega. </event>
      <event start="T871-881" end="T366">Ma, </event>
      <event start="T366" end="T873-514">nekaj ga je. </event>
      <event start="T877-667" end="T878-754">Tisto je še prezgodaj. T() </event>
      <event start="T878-754" end="T879-919">tisto more biti toplo, </event>
      <event start="T879-919" end="T880-329">ne? </event>
      <event start="T885-507" end="T887-822">Ja, pa imajo že sadikice cvetače? </event>
      <event start="T889-063" end="T889-553">Aja? </event>
      <event start="T892-498" end="T893-966">Pa kje si ti to vse videla? </event>
      <event start="T895-705" end="T896-844">A, </event>
      <event start="T896-844" end="T897-586">pol moram iti jaz jutri pogledat. </event>
      <event start="T899-311" end="T900-695">Bom šla čez vikend pol j() eee, </event>
      <event start="T900-695" end="T902-49">seveda če ne bo dežja. </event>
      <event start="T904-84" end="T336">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T336" end="T905-87">zato ker je še mraz, ne? </event>
      <event start="T908-109" end="T908-701">Ne. </event>
      <event start="T908-701" end="T910-739">Tisto rata pol vse rumeno tako. </event>
      <event start="T911-855" end="T912-216">Aja? </event>
      <event start="T913-985" end="T914-67">Aja? </event>
      <event start="T914-67" end="T915-659">Kaj pa brokoli? </event>
      <event start="T918-371" end="T918-752">Aja? </event>
      <event start="T923-271" end="T339">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T339" end="T924-346">tisto imamo radi. </event>
      <event start="T932-743" end="T934-459">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T934-459" end="T935-590">da je pol vsakega malo. </event>
      <event start="T938-404" end="T938-861">Ne? </event>
      <event start="T944-074" end="T288">Ni samo ena korenika, </event>
      <event start="T288" end="T946-008">jih je več. </event>
      <event start="T950-597" end="T951-135">Aja? </event>
      <event start="T952-448" end="T956-439">Ma kaj to je res, da se da h korenčku lahko tudi mivko? </event>
      <event start="T965-491" end="T374">Aha, </event>
      <event start="T374" end="T966-216">rabi biti bolj mehka zemlja. </event>
      <event start="T966-216" end="T969-11">Da lahko naredi koreniko. </event>
      <event start="T972-55" end="T973-775">Da je čim več belega? </event>
      <event start="T975-927" end="T342">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T342" end="T977-782">Tisto je fino. </event>
      <event start="T983-472" end="T210">Pa kaj naj pol kupim, </event>
      <event start="T210" end="T986-524">tudi loke pa tisto kopreno? </event>
      <event start="T991-362" end="T343">Ja, kaj, </event>
      <event start="T343" end="T992-66">zimska je bolj debela, </event>
      <event start="T992-66" end="T993-332">so različne? </event>
      <event start="T996-483" end="T997-347">Aja, dve? </event>
      <event start="T1001-328" end="T1002-45">A različne so? </event>
      <event start="T1009-463" end="T1011-278">Da bi [nerazumljivo] kaj? </event>
      <event start="T1014-352" end="T1015-008">Ne, to ne morem, </event>
      <event start="T1015-008" end="T1016-763">ko nisem vsak dan tam. </event>
      <event start="T1023-575" end="T1024-237">Aja. </event>
      <event start="T1024-587" end="T1025-231">Pol pa boljše, da dam kopreno, </event>
      <event start="T1025-231" end="T1026-746">ko diha. </event>
      <event start="T1035-701" end="T1036-387">Mhm. </event>
      <event start="T1040-346" end="T1042-498">Ja, češplje bom sadila. </event>
      <event start="T1043-376" end="T220">Pa m() pa to, </event>
      <event start="T220" end="T221">kaj je že, </event>
      <event start="T221" end="T1047-132">češnjo. </event>
      <event start="T1047-132" end="T1048-391">To bi še dala. </event>
      <event start="T1049-275" end="T1051-523">Ne, češnjo ta pravo, da bo sadež. </event>
      <event start="T1052-914" end="T1054-576">Bom naredila kakšno marmelado pol. </event>
      <event start="T1058-975" end="T279">Aja? </event>
      <event start="T279" end="T1061-829">Pa kaj, se ne da nič zaščititi? </event>
      <event start="T1066-01" end="T1066-875">Aja. </event>
      <event start="T1072-362" end="T1073-684">Aja, </event>
      <event start="T1073-684" end="T1075-227">to sem imela v planu, da bi še kupila. </event>
      <event start="T1082-506" end="T348">Aja, </event>
      <event start="T348" end="T292">kaj pa to, </event>
      <event start="T292" end="T228">veš, kaj bi jaz dala v dve gredice? </event>
      <event start="T228" end="T383">One dalije, rože, </event>
      <event start="T383" end="T1087-72">ko so mi lepe. </event>
      <event start="T1087-72" end="T1089-833">Tisto tudi ni še zdaj cajt, ne? </event>
      <event start="T1091-826" end="T1093-459">[nerazumljivo] </event>
      <event start="T1108-441" end="T1110-248">A pol bo vsako leto jih več? </event>
      <event start="T1112-954" end="T1114-96">Aha. No, no. </event>
      <event start="T1114-96" end="T232">To bom dala, ja. </event>
      <event start="T232" end="T1117-456">Te so mi lepe. </event>
      <event start="T1117-456" end="T1119-706">Da bom imela za dati si v vazo. </event>
      <event start="T1119-706" end="T1120-77">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1120-77" end="T1122-088">Pa kakšne bi lahko še dala? </event>
      <event start="T1124-56" end="T1125-678">A to je seme pride? </event>
      <event start="T1141-038" end="T1141-921">No, no. </event>
      <event start="T1149-351" end="T1151-681">Pa kaj je to seme tako slabo ratalo? </event>
      <event start="T1152-432" end="T1153-958">Pa še malo dajo noter. </event>
      <event start="T1163-394" end="T1163-763">Aja? </event>
      <event start="T1167-669" end="T1168-578">Aja? </event>
      <event start="T1171-491" end="T1172-462">Ja, ja, ja. </event>
      <event start="T1173-274" end="T1174-523">Pa tudi odganja? </event>
      <event start="T1188-294" end="T1189-681">Ja, da je pol, da </event>
      <event start="T1189-681" end="T1190-514">da je pol lep vrt. </event>
      <event start="T1191-584" end="T1194-160">No. </event>
    </tier>
